            = 0.19765032

P(exactly 8) = 1 × (0.70)⁸ × 1
            = 0.05764801
            = 0.05764801

P(Y₇ < 27.3) = 0.19765032 + 0.05764801
             = 0.25529833
             ≈ 0.2553

Summary: The final answer is $0.255$
