- The CDF of Y₂ is: F_{Y₂}(y) = [1 - e^(-y/2)]²
- The PDF is: f_{Y₂}(y) = 2[1 - e^(-y/2)] · (1/2)e^(-y/2) = [1 - e^(-y/2)]e^(-y/2)

